            0
          
        
        ,
        a
        )
      
    
    {\displaystyle \theta \sim Pa(\theta _{0},a)}
  , then the posterior is also Pareto distributed, and the Bayes estimator under MSE is given by
  
    
      
        
          
            
              θ
              ^
            
          
        
        (
        X
        )
        =
        
          
            
              (
              a
              +
              n
              )
              max
              
                (
                
                  θ
                  
